{"article_id":"9WB8n4VYu2CcaGRs","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"With less than a week to go","depth":10},{"id":1,"text":"until another potential partial federal government shutdown begins on Friday ,","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"bipartisan compromise talks on funding for President Trump 's proposed border wall have completely broken down ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"sources tell Fox News .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"The sudden development again raised the possibility","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"that Trump will declare a national emergency","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"to access previously appropriated funds","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"to initiate construction on a border wall .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"The White House agreed to a temporary spending bill late last month","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to end a historic 35-day government shutdown ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"although Trump said at the time","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"that the move was not a `` concession ''","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"and that he would not relent on his demands for a wall .","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"`` Talks have broken down","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"because Senate Republicans are refusing to compromise on limits to the Trump administration ' s cruel immigration policies , ''","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"a senior Democratic aide told Fox News on Sunday .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"`` A deal","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"that includes new physical barriers","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"must also include limits on the number of ICE detention beds .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"If Senate Republicans won ' t compromise with us on both ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"we can ' t reach a deal . \"","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"Added a GOP source :","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"`` The wall is a red herring for the Democrats .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"We got stuck on an interior enforcement cap . ''","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Such a cap would effectively limit ICE 's ability","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"to house illegal immigrants","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"caught domestically","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"by reducing the number of available beds in detention centers .","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"The goal ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"Democrats say ,","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"is to force the Trump administration to prioritize arresting and deporting only violent criminals and dangerous offenders .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Fox News is told","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"if negotiators can ' t resolve the situation soon ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"they are likely looking at trying to pass another temporary continuing resolution","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to try to avoid a shutdown .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Speaking on `` Fox News Sunday , '' Senate Appropriations Committee Chairman Richard Shelby , R-Ala. ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"who is leading negotiations on border wall funding ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Republicans do n't want to offer concessions on ICE enforcement .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"the talks are stalled right now .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"I ' m hoping","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"we can get off the dime later today or in the morning ,","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"because time is ticking away ,","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"but we ' ve got some problems with the Democrats","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"dealing with ICE ,","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"that is detaining criminals","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"that come into the U.S.","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"and they want a cap on them , ''","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"Shelby said .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"`` We don ' t want a cap on that . ''","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"In response to the news , Trump suggested on Sunday","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"that Democrats are hoping to force another shutdown .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"`` I don ' t think","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"the Dems on the Border Committee are being allowed by their leaders to make a deal , ''","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Trump wrote ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"referring to the bipartisan congressional committee","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"working on a compromise .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"`` They are offering very little money for the desperately needed Border Wall","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"& now , out of the blue , want a cap on convicted violent felons","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"to be held in detention ! ''","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Trump added :","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"`` It was a very bad week for the Democrats , with the GREAT economic numbers , The Virginia disaster and the State of the Union address .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Now , with the terrible offers","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"being made by them to the Border Committee ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"I actually believe","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"they want a Shutdown .","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"They want a new subject ! ''","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"As recently as last Friday , congressional negotiators said","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"they expected a deal to be made ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"although some key players were pessimistic","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"and Democrats indicated","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that money for physical barriers would likely end up well below the $ 5.7 billion","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that Trump has sought","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to begin construction of the wall .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"DEMS PREVIOUSLY SUPPORTED FAR MORE EXPENSIVE SECURE FENCE ACT","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"-- WHAT CHANGED ?","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"The amount","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"discussed","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"hovered much closer to $ 1.6 billion ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"participants in the negotiations said ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"a figure","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that was in a bipartisan Senate bill last year .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"`` That 's what we 're working toward , ''","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"said California Democratic Rep. Lucille Roybal-Allard .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Speaking separately to `` Fox News Sunday , '' Acting Chief of Staff Mick Mulvaney said","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"that an emergency declaration might not be required .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"`` There are other funds of money","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"that are available to [ Trump ]","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"through something","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"called reprogramming ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"there is money","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"he can get at","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"and is legally allowed to spend , ''","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Mulvaney said ,","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"that some funds were available","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"even without declaring an emergency .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"`` And I think","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"it needs to be said again and again","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"this is going to be legal -- -","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"there are statutes on the book","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"as to how any president can do this . ''","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"Still , Mulvaney asserted","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"that a national emergency was `` absolutely on the table ''","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"that a wall will be built , one way or another .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"`` The president is going to build the wall , ''","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Mulvaney said .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"`` You saw what the Vice President said there ,","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"and that ' s our attitude at this point , is we will take as much money","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"as you can give us","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"and then we will go find money someplace else legally","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"in order to secure that southern barrier .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"But this is going to get built with or without Congress . ''","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"Earlier this weekend , Democrats seemed to draw a firm line on spending .","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"`` Throughout the talks , Democrats have insisted","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"that a border security compromise not be overly reliant on physical barriers , ''","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"said Evan Hollander , spokesman for Democrats","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"who control the House Appropriations Committee .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"`` We will not agree to $ 2 billion in funding for barriers . ''","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"The White House has previously offered a three-year extension of protections for 700,000 Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"( DACA )","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"recipients , in exchange for the $ 5.7 billion","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"Trump has been seeking for a barrier along the nation 's southern border with Mexico .","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"The offered deal would also extend protections for 300,000 recipients of the Temporary Protected Status","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"( TPS )","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"program --","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"which protects immigrants from designated countries with conditions","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"that prevent nationals from returning safely .","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"But Democrats have called the border wall nothing more than a political stunt","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"that they will never agree to fund ,","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"while Republicans point to what they have called a `` crisis '' at the border .","depth":5},{"id":133,"text":"Central Americans are increasingly entering the United States illegally in groups of at least 100 people in rugged , remote stretches of the Mexican border ,","depth":5},{"id":134,"text":"authorities said Friday","depth":5},{"id":135,"text":"upon releasing January figures","depth":5},{"id":136,"text":"that show","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"total arrests fell for a second straight month .","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"TRUMP TO PELOSI :","depth":5},{"id":139,"text":"IF WALLS ARE IMMORAL ,","depth":6},{"id":140,"text":"WHY NOT TEAR DOWN EXISTING WALLS TOO ?","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"`` The president is going to build the wall . ''","depth":5},{"id":142,"text":"- Acting White House Chief of Staff Mick Mulvaney","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"A group of 325 Central Americans surrendered to agents Thursday near Lukeville , Ariz. ,","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"according to Customs and Border Protection .","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"Migrants told authorities","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"that buses and trucks dropped them off throughout the night on a nearby Mexican highway","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"that runs parallel to the border","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"and they entered the U.S. together","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"to wait for agents to find them .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"There were nearly 150 children ,","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"including 32","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"who were traveling alone .","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"The Border Patrol has encountered groups of at least 100 people 60 times since Oct. 1 ,","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"compared to 13 during the entire 2018 fiscal year and two in the 2017 fiscal year ,","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"officials said .","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"Many are in the desolate New Mexico Bootheel and Arizona deserts .","depth":6},{"id":157,"text":"It is unclear what 's driving the sudden uptick of large groups in remote areas ,","depth":5},{"id":158,"text":"but families , many of them Central American asylum seekers , make up a large and growing percentage of arrests across the border .","depth":5},{"id":159,"text":"U.S. authorities arrested or stopped people for immigration violations 58,207 times in January , down 4 percent from 60,779 in December but up 62 percent from 35,905 in January 2018 .","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"It was the second straight monthly decline ,","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"though arrests typically fall from December to January .","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"Families and children","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"traveling alone","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"accounted for 33,861 of those encounters ,","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"or nearly 6 of every 10","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"stopped at official crossings or arrested","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"for entering the country illegally between crossings , mostly from Guatemala , El Salvador and Honduras .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"That 's a dramatic change from several years ago ,","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"when most people","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"who crossed illegally","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"were single Mexican adults .","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"The large percentage of families and young children has stretched U.S. authorities even more in remote areas","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"where staffing is thinner .","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"Customs and Border Protection says","depth":6},{"id":175,"text":"medical attention was needed about 12,000 times for border crossers in the 12-month period","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"ending Sept. 30 .","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"On Jan. 14 , a group of 376 Central Americans was arrested near San Luis , Ariz.","depth":5},{"id":178,"text":",","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"the vast majority of them Guatemalan families","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"who dug short , shallow holes under a barrier","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"to cross the border ,","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"according to authorities .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":365,"left":315,"right":364,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":315,"left":297,"right":314,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pa